channel.title: I have not been here in a while! Hello!
channel.description:
Just wanted to stop by and say hi to anyone that might recognize me! How is everyone? :)
I have not been making as much music as I used to. I had around 10 promising tracks that I was working on that I let go stale these past 2 years. I don’t even think I could keep working on them if I wanted to.
